title: near UCSF 3bed/2bath newer building
map_address: 1747 8th Ave unit A near Moraga st
posting_body: ['Built in 1999, this quiet 3 unit building is located in the upscale neighborhood of the goldengate heights.', " The building's exterior has just been painted and the roof has just been worked on a few months ago.", 'It is conveniently located near several public transportation lines, such as Forest Hill MUNI station, N-Judah train, buses 44, 43, and 66, etc.', 'An easy walk to UCSF, the Grandview park for the panoramic view of the city and the famous mosaic staires on 15th ave, walking distance to the Golden Gate Park, Kezar stadium, Irving street shopping and dining.', 'The middle unit has 3 UCSF medical students who are quiet, clean and considerate.', 'The bottom unit is occupied by a very nice couple who work the back yard and enjoy it.', 'However, this top unit has no access to the back yard.', 'Laundry is in the garage and is shared by all tenants.', 'We are looking for folks who are considerate with good credit scores.', 'Note: pictures of Bedrooms are from before the carpets were replaced with hardwood floors.', 'No more carpets in the apartment but area rugs are expected from tenants.', 'A couple of years old side by side stainless steel refrigerator.', '  Hardly used dishwasher.', ' Granite counter tops, double pane windows.', 'Two closets in master bedroom.', '  Jacuzzi in master bathroom can be converted into shower if desired.', 'Large indoor garage and driveway parking available for additional $200 a month.', 'Please tell me a bit about yourself, how many of you, and when you plan to move if you are interested.', 'Thank you!', 'See attached video below: <URL>', 'Andrea Yang DRE #01069969']
